  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat, until it reaches 350°F.",
    "Add the ground oats to the skillet and fry, stirring constantly, until they are lightly browned and crispy, about 5 minutes.",
    "Remove the oats from the skillet and transfer them to a plate.",
    "In a bowl, mix together the beaten egg, crumbled feta, smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper."
